<h2>About</h2>

<p>
  The goal of the Open Source Remote Ventilator Project is to
  quickly develop a lightweight, interoperable remote monitoring
  interface for low-cost rapidly-manufactured ventilators currently
  being developed to provide emergency relief in the Covid-19 Pandemic.
</p>

<p>
  This software is not approved to be used in a medical setting.
</p>

<p>
  <strong>Contribute:</strong>
  Submit an issue or pull request on our <a href="https://github.com/Open-Ventilator-Remote-Monitoring">GitHub</a>
</p>

